Author: blackjok3r#3181
Content: The withdraw object contains the result... Only need validating once, then .It can be hashed and passed from one vout to another

Author: blackjok3r#3181
Content: Compare hash, don't need to validate wit twice

Author: blackjok3r#3181
Content: The initial validation will be slow especially with a million utxos. But once the game is over the winner can just keep withdrawing with no overhead

Author: blackjok3r#3181
Content: No need to merge

Author: blackjok3r#3181
Content: I was going to make it so that if u sent coins to the game after it was over u could reclaim them, but meh, it takes like 20 blocks after the timestamp is over to get the result, sending there is suicide

Author: blackjok3r#3181
Content: Once result is known, any coins in the address are owned by the winner
